# Multilanguage Structure

## URL Structure

The website follows a language-in-path approach with translated slugs:

- **English (default)**: Original content with no language prefix
  ```
  https://kirill-markin.com/articles/cursor-ide-rules-for-ai/
  ```

- **Other languages**: Include language code prefix and localized path segments
  ```
  https://kirill-markin.com/es/articulos/reglas-cursor-ide-para-ia/
  https://kirill-markin.com/hi/लेख/cursor-ide-के-लिए-नियम/
  ```

