## SEO Implementation

All pages must include proper hreflang annotations to help search engines understand language relationships:

```html
<!-- For current page (e.g., Spanish) -->
<link rel="canonical" href="https://kirill-markin.com/es/articulos/reglas-cursor-ide-para-ia/" />

<!-- For all language alternatives -->
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://kirill-markin.com/articles/cursor-ide-rules-for-ai/" />
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="es" href="https://kirill-markin.com/es/articulos/reglas-cursor-ide-para-ia/" />
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="hi" href="https://kirill-markin.com/hi/लेख/cursor-ide-के-लिए-नियम/" />

<!-- Default version -->
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://kirill-markin.com/articles/cursor-ide-rules-for-ai/" />
```

