## Implementation Guidelines

1. All new content must be created in English first
2. Translations should maintain the same content structure but can adapt cultural references
3. URL slugs should be optimized for SEO in each language
4. The sitemap must include all language variations with proper hreflang references
5. Language switcher UI should be present on all pages
6. Always connect translations to originals via metadata
7. Static generation should be used for all language versions
